			<m:divide/>
			<m:ci>T</m:ci>
			<m:ci>N</m:ci>
		      </m:apply>
		    </m:apply>
		  </m:math>).  How should
		  <m:math><m:ci>N</m:ci></m:math> be related to
		  <m:math><m:ci>B</m:ci></m:math>, the number of
		  simultaneously transmitted bits?</item>

		<item>The alumni wants to find a simple form for the
